              <h1>Peter Wilmshurst</h1>
              <p>
                I am a senior frontend developer with 12+ years of commercial
                experience. I’m interested in all kinds of visual communication,
                but my major focus is on the design and development of web,
                mobile and tablet interfaces. I am enthusiastic, self-motivated
                and extremely driven with a wide range of skills both in terms
                of design and development.
              </p>

